        Method to return WebJar resources matching AntPathMatcher patterns.
        Parameters:
        useCdn - true to provide a CDN URI; false for a local path.
        scheme - The URI scheme.
        patterns - The AntPathMatcher patterns to match.

      • cdn

        public String cdn(String scheme,
                  String path)
        Method to convert a WebJar resource (partial) path to its corresponding CDN (URI) path. Typical Thymeleaf usage: @{${#webjars.cdn(#request.scheme, path)}}.
        Parameters:
        scheme - The URI scheme.
        path - The (possibly partial) path.
        Returns:
        The CDN URI if one may be constructed; path otherwise.
